38:29.380 --> 38:30.971
Hey. How was dinner?

38:31.449 --> 38:33.352
Good. Yeah, good.

38:34.652 --> 38:35.667
Great.

39:06.975 --> 39:08.574
What do you need me to do?

39:16.508 --> 39:18.027
I have to go to Toronto.

39:20.567 --> 39:22.378
We'll talk when I get back.

39:41.319 --> 39:43.119
- Yeah?
- Okay, look, I know

39:43.187 --> 39:44.687
that you said that you were done...

39:44.756 --> 39:47.157
- And I meant it. <i>
- There's a name.</i>

39:47.658 --> 39:49.792
It should be in the IHM system.

39:49.861 --> 39:51.113
Julie Woolth.

39:51.596 --> 39:53.796
<i>- Can you try to locate her?</i>
- Megan.

39:53.865 --> 39:55.987
It's the last thing I'm
going to ask you to do.

39:56.089 --> 39:57.235
I promise.

39:58.339 --> 39:59.347
Okay.

